flowchart LR
    L[load ledger] --> G[1. Generate<br/>propose sub-questions]
    G --> D[2. Dedup<br/>drop already-asked]
    D --> R[3. Research<br/>sub-agent answers each<br/>→ writes to vault]
    R --> RF[4. Reflect<br/>new answers spawn follow-ups]
    RF --> S{5. Novelty<br/>decayed?}
    S -->|no| L
    S -->|yes| STOP[stop · disable schedule]
